milestones.description: This is the lowest match aggregate (309) involving teams New Zealand & India in ODIs
Glenn Turner has scored 3 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for NZ breaking Bevan Congdon's record
Glenn Turner has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (12) for NZ, going past Hastings
Eknath Solkar has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (6) for IND, going past Syed Abid Ali
Glenn Turner and Jock Edwards's 73-run partnership is NZ's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 51 between Glenn Turner and John Morrison
